      ****************************************************************
      *                                                              *
      *  AREA DE LINKAGE DA ROTINA TRG10000                          *
      *                                                              *
      ****************************************************************
      *

       01  TGCL1000-LENGTH                       PIC  9(05) VALUE 200.
       01  TGCL1000-NR-CAMPOS                    PIC  9(05) VALUE 5.
      *
       01  TGCL1000-MSG.
           05 TGCL1000-ASE.
              10 TGCL1000-CTABELA-ST.
                 15 TGCL1000-CTABELA-S         PIC  X(01).
                    88 TGCL1000-CTABELA-0      VALUE '0'.
                    88 TGCL1000-CTABELA-1      VALUE '1' ' '.
                 15 TGCL1000-CTABELA-CAPLIC    PIC X(02).
                 15 TGCL1000-CTABELA-MSG       PIC 9(04).

              10 TGCL1000-CCOD-ST.
                 15 TGCL1000-CCOD-S         PIC  X(01).
                    88 TGCL1000-CCOD-0      VALUE '0'.
                    88 TGCL1000-CCOD-1      VALUE '1' ' '.
                 15 TGCL1000-CCOD-CAPLIC    PIC X(02).
                 15 TGCL1000-CCOD-MSG       PIC 9(04).

              10 TGCL1000-C2COD-ST.
                 15 TGCL1000-C2COD-S         PIC  X(01).
                    88 TGCL1000-C2COD-0      VALUE '0'.
                    88 TGCL1000-C2COD-1      VALUE '1' ' '.
                 15 TGCL1000-C2COD-CAPLIC    PIC X(02).
                 15 TGCL1000-C2COD-MSG       PIC 9(04).

              10 TGCL1000-CLINGUA-ST.
                 15 TGCL1000-CLINGUA-S         PIC  X(01).
                    88 TGCL1000-CLINGUA-0      VALUE '0'.
                    88 TGCL1000-CLINGUA-1      VALUE '1' ' '.
                 15 TGCL1000-CLINGUA-CAPLIC    PIC X(02).
                 15 TGCL1000-CLINGUA-MSG       PIC 9(04).

              10 TGCL1000-GDESC-ST.
                 15 TGCL1000-GDESC-S         PIC  X(01).
                    88 TGCL1000-GDESC-0      VALUE '0'.
                    88 TGCL1000-GDESC-1      VALUE '1' ' '.
                 15 TGCL1000-GDESC-CAPLIC    PIC X(02).
                 15 TGCL1000-GDESC-MSG       PIC 9(04).

      *
          05  TGCL1000-ADE.
                10 TGCL1000-CACCAO  PIC X(01).
                10 TGCL1000-CTABELA PIC X(05).
                10 TGCL1000-CTABELA-R REDEFINES TGCL1000-CTABELA.
                  15 TGCL1000-CTABELA-TIPO        PIC X(02).
                  15 FILLER                       PIC X(03).
                10 TGCL1000-CCOD PIC X(50).
                10 TGCL1000-C2COD PIC X(50).
                10 TGCL1000-CLINGUA PIC X(10).
                10 TGCL1000-GDESC PIC X(50).
      *
       01  TGCL1000-ROTINA              PIC  X(10) VALUE 'TGR10000'.
       01  TGCL1000-ROTINA-2            PIC  X(10) VALUE 'TG2R1000'.

